到自己)<br />\n所以d通識都幾勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n我同你都幾似<br />\n又係中三開始知自己想要啲咩 想做啲咩 可能比同年齡既女仔仲快諗過將來要讀乜做乜 到而家考完dse衰咗科主科都仲係堅持要讀返上去 <br />\n有時真係倔強到人地勸自己唔好做嗰樣野又係死都要做<br />\n一樣係跟好曬規劃 唔亂得嗰啲人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6464bd2bcfa966cdfe3c7cfaeb6d1dec9807cf7d","tid":522260,"uid":165872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"71c903181925220ace67af8c7e2ae24d96ba08c8","tid":522260,"uid":36237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0697e315f0a99e27e57458538495d9db136bebc0","tid":522260,"uid":165872,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1b254655dc47552aca591eec0a90ae5d8fe099dc","tid":522260,"uid":36237,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T13:01:15.000Z","msg":"我係山羊女 基本上同上面講既好似<br />\n都係好有規劃 個個朋友都覺得我太過規劃前面既野 好似中二三已經知道知道中學畢業要讀乜做乜(雖然最後乜都唔同曬變曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n做野好跟規劃 一就一二就二<br />\n所有野都要求自己跟足時間<br />\n同所有野都要分析得好仔細(雖然有時候真係仔細到無謂又傷到自己)<br />\n所以d通識都幾勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T13:02:31.000Z","msg":"我反而唔係咁 好迷惘 成日都唔知自己做緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T13:08:30.000Z","msg":"我都有識山羊女咩都唔知要人決定 唔會個個一樣既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T13:34:05.000Z","msg":"都係嘅 不過摩羯座真係好天真 好易信人 俾人利用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d5a0e6b99ff56de1971dfa79ff067a3530944b","tid":522260,"uid":36237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6464bd2bcfa966cdfe3c7cfaeb6d1dec9807cf7d","tid":522260,"uid":165872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"71c903181925220ace67af8c7e2ae24d96ba08c8","tid":522260,"uid":36237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0697e315f0a99e27e57458538495d9db136bebc0","tid":522260,"uid":165872,"like"